<lb n="2" break="no"/>drisaṁvatsarada sravaṇa ba 5 bri
<lb n="3"/>śrīkalidēvara nityapaḍi vuphāra naṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dādīvige vijñēsvara kṣētrapāḷa nā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rāyaṇadēvara <unclear>va</unclear>sudhāreya
<lb n="6"/>naḍasalu gaṇapiseṭṭiyara maga śrīma
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nmahāpradhānaṁ vīriseṭiyaru Era
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ya keya kaṁba yipatumaṁ kalyāṇi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dēvarige dhārāpūrvvakavāgi koṭṭa dharmma
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vaṁ Eṟakaga <supplied reason="omitted">vu</supplied>ḍa<unclear>nu</unclear> hegaḍe <unclear>sēna</unclear> prati pālisu
<lb n="11" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>ru maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī śrī
